Variants keep your JSX clean and animations reusable.

---

## Gesture Animations with Type Safety

```typescript
import { motion, PanInfo } from 'framer-motion';

const DraggableCard = () => {
  const handleDragEnd = (
    event: MouseEvent | TouchEvent | PointerEvent,
    info: PanInfo
  ) => {
